  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/d0e9b09fd6cabf321baed76fb2e90b56.avif?t=1722518032\" width=614 height=158 /></span><br><br><strong><i>睁开眼的那一刻，一切都变了...</i></strong><br><br>我叫<strong><i>白笙</i></strong>，不愿和你提起我赖以生存的家园因何至此，现在我唯一要做的，是考虑<strong><u>自己</u></strong>如何生存...<br>幸运的是，政府并没有放弃我，只要我能安全到达疏散点，一切都会好起来吧...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >初见</h2>“Fla..Fla..”<br>在“沃姆市”某处遇见的女孩仍然跟着我，可她不知道，我向来做事只顾自己，如果不是刚才那该死的同情心突然泛滥..<br>得想个办法摆脱她才行...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/a4e968244e525598bdcda300bc83887a.poster.avif?t=1722518032\" width=672 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/a4e968244e525598bdcda300bc83887a.webm?t=1722518032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/a4e968244e525598bdcda300bc83887a.mp4?t=1722518032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人性</h2>“喂，站住！”<br>猛然回头，不知何时，几个发型怪异的男人正往我这边走来，我的直觉告诉我，他们或许不是善茬。<br>我应该撒腿就跑？但如果我跑不过他们..我可能活不下来<br>我应该乖乖就范？或许主动把钱和食物交给他们能有一线生机吧...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/535f2461aae3b34bec4a610c81b54ed7.poster.avif?t=1722518032\" width=672 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/535f2461aae3b34bec4a610c81b54ed7.webm?t=1722518032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/535f2461aae3b34bec4a610c81b54ed7.mp4?t=1722518032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >曙光</h2>“汪！汪！汪！”<br>是啊，它们也多久没吃过肉了——看着奔我而来的恶犬，我已经想好自己将面临什么了...<br>但，石堆突然落下，恶犬被掩埋在石海中...是谁还来拯救我这样懦弱自私的人？<br>“Fla..Fla..”<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/114c196a29458741ca65537866ef4fa4.poster.avif?t=1722518032\" width=672 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/114c196a29458741ca65537866ef4fa4.webm?t=1722518032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/114c196a29458741ca65537866ef4fa4.mp4?t=1722518032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >救赎</h2>“昨天抓的妞脾气很倔啊”<br>“要不你去试试？”<br>“我来我来...”<br>不堪入耳的话语从营地传来，这里似乎是强盗们的聚集地？我抄起石头就往前走去...向来懦弱的我，现在却因有了寄托而变得勇敢...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/a6ec3e6916b4342ba736a8abca9b4e28.poster.avif?t=1722518032\" width=672 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/a6ec3e6916b4342ba736a8abca9b4e28.webm?t=1722518032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/a6ec3e6916b4342ba736a8abca9b4e28.mp4?t=1722518032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>我叫<strong><i>白笙</i></strong>，不愿和你提起我们赖以生存的家园因何至此，现在我唯一要做的，是考虑<strong><u>我们</u></strong>如何生存...",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/d0e9b09fd6cabf321baed76fb2e90b56.avif?t=1722518032\" width=614 height=158 /></span><br><br><strong><i>睁开眼的那一刻，一切都变了...</i></strong><br><br>我叫<strong><i>白笙</i></strong>，不愿和你提起我赖以生存的家园因何至此，现在我唯一要做的，是考虑<strong><u>自己</u></strong>如何生存...<br>幸运的是，政府并没有放弃我，只要我能安全到达疏散点，一切都会好起来吧...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >初见</h2>“Fla..Fla..”<br>在“沃姆市”某处遇见的女孩仍然跟着我，可她不知道，我向来做事只顾自己，如果不是刚才那该死的同情心突然泛滥..<br>得想个办法摆脱她才行...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/a4e968244e525598bdcda300bc83887a.poster.avif?t=1722518032\" width=672 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/a4e968244e525598bdcda300bc83887a.webm?t=1722518032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/a4e968244e525598bdcda300bc83887a.mp4?t=1722518032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人性</h2>“喂，站住！”<br>猛然回头，不知何时，几个发型怪异的男人正往我这边走来，我的直觉告诉我，他们或许不是善茬。<br>我应该撒腿就跑？但如果我跑不过他们..我可能活不下来<br>我应该乖乖就范？或许主动把钱和食物交给他们能有一线生机吧...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/535f2461aae3b34bec4a610c81b54ed7.poster.avif?t=1722518032\" width=672 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/535f2461aae3b34bec4a610c81b54ed7.webm?t=1722518032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669330/extras/535f2461aae3b34bec4a610c81b54ed7.mp4?t=1722518032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >曙光</h2>“汪！汪！汪！”<br>是啊，它们也多久没吃过肉了——看着